comment: /**  * Set the default value, used if no value is set by the command-line  * configuration.  *  * @param defaultValue the default value  * @return this  */
code: /**  * Set the default value, used if no value is set by the command-line  * configuration.  *  * @param defaultValue the default value  * @return this  */ protected SimpleParameter setDefaultValue(T defaultValue) {     this.hasDefaultValue = true.     this.defaultValue = defaultValue.     return this. }
@Override public String getUsage() {     String option = "--" + name + " " + name.toUpperCase().     return hasDefaultValue ? "[" + option + "]" : option. }
